<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Việc của tôi - WA_PM</title>

    <style>
        /* --- Main Layout --- */
        .main-wrapper {
            margin-left: var(--sidebar-width);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* --- Topbar --- */
        .topbar {
            height: var(--topbar-height);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 0 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: white;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        /* --- My Work Header & Tabs --- */
        .work-header {
            padding: 40px 40px 0;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .work-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .nav-tabs {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .nav-link {
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            margin-bottom: -1px;
        }

            .nav-link:hover {
                color: var(--primary-color);
                border-color: transparent;
            }

            .nav-link.active {
                color: var(--primary-color);
                background: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            }

        /* --- Work Content --- */
        .work-content {
            padding: 24px 40px;
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        /* Filter Bar */
        .filter-bar {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .search-input {
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Issue Table */
        .issue-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0;
        }

            .issue-table th {
                text-align: left;
                padding: 8px 16px;
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--text-secondary);
                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            }

            .issue-table td {
                padding: 12px 16px;
                border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
                vertical-align: middle;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

        .issue-row:hover td {
            background-color: #f7f8f9;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Table Cells Styling */
        .col-type {
            width: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .col-key {
            width: 100px;
        }

        .col-summary {
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .col-project {
            width: 180px;
        }

        .col-status {
            width: 140px;
        }

        .col-prio {
            width: 100px;
        }

        .col-due {
            width: 120px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .type-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: white;
        }

        .bg-story {
            background-color: #36b37e;
        }

        .bg-bug {
            background-color: #ff5630;
        }

        .bg-task {
            background-color: #0c66e4;
        }

        .issue-key {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .issue-summary {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .issue-row:hover .issue-summary {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .project-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .project-color {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .status-todo {
            background-color: #dfe1e6;
            color: #42526e;
        }

        .status-progress {
            background-color: #deebff;
            color: #0052cc;
        }

        .status-done {
            background-color: #e3fcef;
            color: #006644;
        }

        .prio-icon {
            margin-right: 4px;
        }

        .prio-high {
            color: #ff5630;
        }

        .prio-med {
            color: #ffab00;
        }

        .prio-low {
            color: #36b37e;
        }

        .due-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .due-overdue {
            color: #bf2600;
            font-weight: 600;
            background-color: #ffebe6;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-wrapper">
        <!-- Topbar -->
        <div class="topbar">
            <div class="page-title">Công việc của tôi</div>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-bell"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Work Header with Tabs -->
        <div class="work-header">
            <h1 class="work-title">Việc được giao (Assigned to me)</h1>
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Current</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Overdue <span class="badge bg-danger rounded-pill ms-1">1</span></a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Completed</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item ms-auto">
                    <!-- Right aligned link if needed -->
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Work Content -->
        <div class="work-content">

            <!-- Filters -->
            <div class="filter-bar">
                <div class="input-group input-group-sm search-input">
                    <span class="input-group-text bg-white border-end-0"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass text-secondary"></i></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control border-start-0" placeholder="Tìm theo tên issue...">
                </div>

                <select class="form-select form-select-sm" style="width: 150px;">
                    <option selected>Tất cả dự án</option>
                    <option>Dự án Alpha</option>
                    <option>Marketing Q4</option>
                    <option>Mobile App Revamp</option>
                </select>

                <select class="form-select form-select-sm" style="width: 150px;">
                    <option selected>Mọi trạng thái</option>
                    <option>To Do</option>
                    <option>In Progress</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <!-- Issues Table -->
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="issue-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="col-type">Type</th>
                            <th class="col-key">Key</th>
                            <th class="col-summary">Summary</th>
                            <th class="col-project">Project</th>
                            <th class="col-status">Status</th>
                            <th class="col-prio">Priority</th>
                            <th class="col-due">Due Date</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <!-- Issue 1: Overdue -->
                        <tr class="issue-row">
                            <td class="col-type">
                                <span class="type-icon bg-bug" title="Bug"><i class="fa-solid fa-bug"></i></span>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="issue-key">ALP-104</span></td>
                            <td><div class="issue-summary">Fix lỗi kết nối SQL Server LocalDB</div></td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="project-badge">
                                    <div class="project-color" style="background-color: #0c66e4;"></div>
                                    Alpha
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="status-badge status-progress">In Progress</span></td>
                            <td><span class="prio-high"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up prio-icon"></i> High</span></td>
                            <td class="text-end"><span class="due-date due-overdue">Today</span></td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- Issue 2: Normal -->
                        <tr class="issue-row">
                            <td class="col-type">
                                <span class="type-icon bg-story" title="Story"><i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark"></i></span>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="issue-key">ALP-103</span></td>
                            <td><div class="issue-summary">Implement trang Login & Register Frontend</div></td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="project-badge">
                                    <div class="project-color" style="background-color: #0c66e4;"></div>
                                    Alpha
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="status-badge status-progress">In Progress</span></td>
                            <td><span class="prio-med"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus prio-icon"></i> Medium</span></td>
                            <td class="text-end"><span class="due-date">30 Dec</span></td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- Issue 3 -->
                        <tr class="issue-row">
                            <td class="col-type">
                                <span class="type-icon bg-task" title="Task"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i></span>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="issue-key">MAR-42</span></td>
                            <td><div class="issue-summary">Update App Icon cho phiên bản iOS mới</div></td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="project-badge">
                                    <div class="project-color" style="background-color: #6554C0;"></div>
                                    Mobile App
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="status-badge status-todo">To Do</span></td>
                            <td><span class="prio-low"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down prio-icon"></i> Low</span></td>
                            <td class="text-end"><span class="due-date">02 Jan</span></td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- Issue 4 -->
                        <tr class="issue-row">
                            <td class="col-type">
                                <span class="type-icon bg-story" title="Story"><i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark"></i></span>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="issue-key">ALP-120</span></td>
                            <td><div class="issue-summary">Viết Unit Test cho UserService</div></td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="project-badge">
                                    <div class="project-color" style="background-color: #0c66e4;"></div>
                                    Alpha
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="status-badge status-todo">To Do</span></td>
                            <td><span class="prio-med"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus prio-icon"></i> Medium</span></td>
                            <td class="text-end"><span class="due-date">05 Jan</span></td>
                        </tr>

                        <!-- Issue 5 -->
                        <tr class="issue-row">
                            <td class="col-type">
                                <span class="type-icon bg-task" title="Task"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i></span>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="issue-key">MKT-15</span></td>
                            <td><div class="issue-summary">Tổng hợp feedback khách hàng Q3</div></td>
                            <td>
                                <div class="project-badge">
                                    <div class="project-color" style="background-color: #00875A;"></div>
                                    Marketing Q4
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td><span class="status-badge status-todo">To Do</span></td>
                            <td><span class="prio-high"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up prio-icon"></i> High</span></td>
                            <td class="text-end"><span class="due-date">08 Jan</span></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <!-- Empty State (Hidden by default, used when no issues) -->
            <div class="text-center py-5 d-none">
                <div style="font-size: 48px; color: #dfe1e6; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i>
                </div>
                <h5>Tuyệt vời! Bạn đã hoàn thành hết công việc.</h5>
                <p class="text-secondary">Hãy thư giãn hoặc tìm kiếm công việc mới trong Backlog.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap Bundle JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>